            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tofu is cooking, combine your <strong>carrot, mooli & pink cabbage slaw mix </strong>with your<strong> mayo </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your<strong> rice vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
