    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe the reserved bowl clean</p><p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter </strong>with your<strong> remaining soy sauce </strong>and<strong> remaining rice vinegar </strong>in<strong> </strong>the reserved bowl until smooth</p><p>Add the <strong>smashed cucumber</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>peanutty smashed cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
