    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cooked rice</strong> in bowls and layer over the <strong>peanutty smashed cucumber</strong>, <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>slaw </strong>and <strong>umami tofu</strong></p><p>Drizzle your <strong>red chilli relish </strong>over the tofu – this is your <strong>sticky sweet chilli tofu bowl and peanutty smashed cucumber</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
